{"tid":416101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比痘印困擾人生","createTime":"2017-09-27T13:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T14:01:07.000Z","uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea43159675949b3e338b43b8e6f1e6c44e805aa","tid":416101,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"細佬小個成日唔洗面又成日食老M，食到成面痘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過左幾年因為真係戒左好多野，所以都無點生痘。留下既就係D痘印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一噠一噠咁，好深色。真係好惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴絲都係咁，可以點解決，人生最青春嗰幾年都無哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs.以家有用手作番梘洗臉"},{"pid":"e57c71481bc4c7c56f4b5cbbf37a2bb71a3312b6","tid":416101,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"覺得手作番梘好唔好用？未用過有想試下"},{"pid":"62516010caab0695d8af7f15b723c8c278571bc7","tid":416101,"uid":64200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"早晚洗完面用暗瘡啫喱 <br />\n早瞓覺<br />\n多飲水（每日最少1.5L清水)<br />\n暗瘡印會由紅變黑 再沉底 經代謝排出<br />\n兩個月自然乜印都冇<br />\n<br />\nsource:個人經驗"},{"pid":"8530c50aa3aae4f66837037428e1fd01019e1fda","tid":416101,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得手作番梘好唔好用？未用過有想試下</blockquote><br />\n有，未用之前D痘印痴埋一舊 成噠疤咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以家起碼正常反+面白左"},{"pid":"9de7cf237583dd08d75e790fb73089ec4854c11a","tid":416101,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早晚洗完面用暗瘡啫喱 <br />\n早瞓覺<br />\n多飲水（每日最少1.5L清水)<br />\n暗瘡印會由紅變黑 再沉底 經代謝排出<br />\n兩個月自然乜印都冇<br />\n<br />\nsource:個人經驗</blockquote><br />\n最大鍋就係黑左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}